SIMULATION OF BALL MACHINE

Introduction

ball machine is used in cricket practicing in absence of bowler.

normally ball machine has fast, slow and bounce option.

we made a future generation ball machine it includes changing sides, swing and spin variations.

Function used-

1) mainly transformation function are used - like translate, rotate.

2) for shapes - primitive, attribute and input functions are used.

3) for printing - glutbitmap character is used.

4) keyboard functions and menus are also used.

Feautures -

1) use keys to assign variation.

2) change sides using menus.

3) if ball hits the wicket bails comes off.

4) proper seam movement fo variations.

